38
00:02:03,080 --> 00:02:03,720
Yes!

39
00:02:05,800 --> 00:02:06,200
Come.

40
00:02:07,880 --> 00:02:08,440
Be careful.

41
00:02:09,160 --> 00:02:09,600
Be careful.

42
00:02:20,920 --> 00:02:21,520
Zixuan.

43
00:02:24,160 --> 00:02:25,800
What's wrong with Zixuan's eyes?

44
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:27,200
I've consulted physicians,

45
00:02:27,200 --> 00:02:28,120
but none

46
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,240
could diagnose.

47
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:34,680
You know something, right?

48
00:02:35,600 --> 00:02:36,600
Tell me.

49
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:38,400
Is this related to the game?

50
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:43,360
Don't panic.

51
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:45,600
How can I not panic?

52
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,160
What is this?

53
00:02:52,440 --> 00:02:54,480
Speak up! What is this?

54
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:59,080
I once believed

55
00:02:59,760 --> 00:03:01,600
that everyone's fate in this world

56
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:03,400
was predetermined.

57
00:03:05,200 --> 00:03:06,120
But I never expected

58
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:08,440
that fate could change.

59
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:11,840
A person without feelings

60
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:13,840
could open up

61
00:03:13,920 --> 00:03:15,440
to another one.

62
00:03:17,160 --> 00:03:18,640
A person without affection

63
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:22,040
could plant seeds
of love for another one.

64
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:25,400
What has happened shows

65
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:29,040
that both your destinies
have transformed.

66
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:30,920
So,

67
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:33,120
from the very beginning,

68
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:38,520
your fates weren't tied to the Top Tea.

69
00:03:53,918 --> 00:03:58,080
(Missions)

70
00:04:02,160 --> 00:04:03,360
We've accomplished the missions

71
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:04,520
required of us.

72
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:08,200
Candlelight illuminates
what eyes can see,

73
00:04:08,920 --> 00:04:10,400
revealing only surface truths.

74
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:12,280
To see deeper

75
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:14,400
requires following your heart.

76
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:16,840
Close your eyes.

77
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:21,440
Let your inner light guide your vision.

78
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,720
(In this world,)

79
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,440
(things change,)

80
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:37,480
(and lives change.)

81
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:44,120
(Love exists. In the sixth year
of Yuanfeng era,)

82
00:04:44,960 --> 00:04:46,560
(Xiaotang, Li Zixuan's wife,)

83
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:48,920
(for some reason,)

84
00:04:49,280 --> 00:04:51,840
(repeatedly saved Zixuan's life.)

85
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:54,600
(Karma changed.)

86
00:04:55,240 --> 00:04:57,000
(Fate changed.)

87
00:04:58,520 --> 00:05:00,840
(The couple sowed their own seeds,)

88
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:03,640
(thus reaping their own harvest.)

89
00:05:04,840 --> 00:05:07,120
(Wei Xiaotang saved Li Zixuan.)

90
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:08,960
(She fell in love.)

91
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:10,880
(It happens naturally.)

92
00:05:12,200 --> 00:05:13,520
(She risked her own life)

93
00:05:13,640 --> 00:05:15,920
(to protect Li Zixuan)

94
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:18,680
(until karma is balanced.)

95
00:05:19,320 --> 00:05:21,240
(From whence it came)

96
00:05:21,960 --> 00:05:24,440
(to whence it returns,)

97
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:28,480
(Li Zixuan's forbidden longing
for Wei Xiaotang)

98
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,560
(produced love.)

99
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:34,800
(He loves her)

100
00:05:35,080 --> 00:05:36,680
(wholeheartedly)

101
00:05:36,760 --> 00:05:38,920
(until debts were repaid.)

102
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:41,520
(Throughout it all,)

103
00:05:41,760 --> 00:05:43,880
(he follows his heart.)

104
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:45,800
(Thus,)

105
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:48,680
(the couple fell in love.)

106
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:50,880
(Apply their strengths,)

107
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:52,560
(and gain mutual recognition.)

108
00:05:53,640 --> 00:05:55,000
(They got rid of Uncle.)

109
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:57,080
(This is a joint effort.)

110
00:05:57,840 --> 00:05:59,800
(They won the tea competition.)

111
00:05:59,880 --> 00:06:01,800
(This is a shared triumph.)

112
00:06:02,840 --> 00:06:04,400
(They took down Mr. Wang.)

113
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:07,560
(This is a life-and-death trial.)

114
00:06:08,440 --> 00:06:09,840
(They resolved family disputes)

115
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:11,760
(and revealed Mother's malice,)

116
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:16,960
(making the couple relieved.)

117
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:20,200
You made a contract.

118
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:21,520
I believed

119
00:06:21,960 --> 00:06:24,800
that you were meant to make the Top Tea.

120
00:06:25,880 --> 00:06:26,960
But I never expected

121
00:06:27,440 --> 00:06:28,280
that your true trial

122
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:30,760
wouldn't be the perilous path
to victory,

123
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:34,960
but a contract
of letting go of each other.

124
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:38,920
Love is selfish,

125
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:41,960
yet true devotion is selfless.

126
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:43,680
You are

127
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,080
selfishly possessive of each other.

128
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:48,040
Meanwhile,
you two selflessly let go of each other.

129
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:50,200
This paradoxical entanglement

130
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:52,000
is your true destiny.

131
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:58,400
Zixuan's blindness
is merely the beginning.

132
00:06:59,640 --> 00:07:01,480
He defied his fate

133
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,560
and selfishly kept you by his side.

134
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:06,160
He will be gone ultimately.

135
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:09,920
To save him,

136
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:12,040
you must leave,

137
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:16,160
selflessly letting go of him.

138
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:17,800
Then,

139
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:20,880
all memories
between you and Zixuan will vanish.

140
00:07:20,880 --> 00:07:23,680
Time will rewind to your wedding night.

141
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:27,160
He will forget everything about you

142
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:29,840
and marry the original Wei Xiaotang,

143
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:31,640
living happily ever after.

144
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:36,200
This is the seed of fate you've sown.

145
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:39,680
Having tasted the fruit of love,

146
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:43,680
you must now
accept the bitter harvest of separation.

147
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:36,800
Xiaotang.

148
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,120
You're back.

149
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:48,600
I'm home.

150
00:08:51,920 --> 00:08:52,600
Could you

151
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:54,440
look at the color of this tea?

152
00:09:01,880 --> 00:09:03,080
It's good.

153
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:16,920
Actually,

154
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:19,720
I don't have to master tea making

155
00:09:20,680 --> 00:09:22,240
as long as I have you.

156
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:29,360
Rest assured,

157
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:32,240
I'll help you restore your sight.

158
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:34,800
I was just out

159
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:37,200
to find you an excellent physician.

160
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:39,160
He'll come tomorrow,

161
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:41,520
and you'll regain your vision soon.

162
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:56,760
What's wrong with you?

163
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:07,760
Xiaotang.

164
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:09,400
What inspired you

165
00:10:09,560 --> 00:10:10,720
to invite us for drinks

166
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:11,920
without Zixuan?

167
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:13,320
Acting all mysterious.

168
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:16,600
Well, I'll be frank with you all.

169
00:10:20,280 --> 00:10:21,840
This is yours.

170
00:10:23,280 --> 00:10:24,120
Here you are.

171
00:10:24,800 --> 00:10:25,520
This...

172
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:27,280
This is my development plan

173
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:28,160
for the tea estate.

174
00:10:28,920 --> 00:10:30,880
I wrote it for Miss Niaoniao

175
00:10:31,560 --> 00:10:33,640
and Mr. Qi.

176
00:10:34,640 --> 00:10:36,280
Plans for Gu's Tea Estate?

177
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:38,200
Oh, Zimo,

178
00:10:38,640 --> 00:10:40,080
read this carefully.

179
00:10:41,040 --> 00:10:41,720
Niaoniao,

180
00:10:42,040 --> 00:10:42,640
watch him.

181
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:44,120
Got it?

182
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:48,000
Xiaotang, you can nag me
at home, not outside.

183
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:51,840
I'll read this at home.

184
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:55,040
Moreover,

185
00:10:55,880 --> 00:10:58,440
you know Zixuan's recent mood

186
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,600
and condition.

187
00:11:00,160 --> 00:11:02,120
So, when you're free,

188
00:11:02,360 --> 00:11:04,680
