208
00:11:46,400 --> 00:11:47,000
Alright.

209
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:48,800
Xiaotang, you eat.

210
00:11:48,800 --> 00:11:49,400
It looks good.

211
00:11:49,400 --> 00:11:50,080
Here, Zimo.

212
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:51,720
You're a grown man.

213
00:11:51,920 --> 00:11:53,800
