Miss, have some fried cakes?

235
00:13:38,280 --> 00:13:39,560
Give it a try!

236
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:49,280
(How is it?)

237
00:13:50,480 --> 00:13:51,280
(Delicious, right?)

